data.title: Gerald R. Ford Birthsite and Gardens
data.meta_description: Walk through the beautiful Memorial Gardens where President Ford's boyhood home once stood. View 9 rosebeds featuring 170 rose bushes and 22 flowerbeds. Open year-round, 7:30am-dusk.
